        "84001": {
          "vnum": 84001,
          "name": "Dry Riverbed",
          "description": "Formerly one of the Chardaleth Sea's lesser tributaries, the Dreck River ceased flowing when Ilarien slew Alestar. Why a river leagues away from Torm Sarvek would expire as well ... that's a mystery only the skies can answer. A trail begins to lead back to Mareldja to the north. To the southeast, the riverbed rises, slowly becoming a field.",
