        "84003": {
          "vnum": 84003,
          "name": "Lone Prairie",
          "description": "It is easy to see how a man might covet this land -- vast, unclaimed, and fertile. Equally easy to miss that the grass and clover were a shade closer to brown than green. A man could surely taste the bountiful harvests to come. An ox-driven plow, some seed, hard work, what else would he need?",
