          "vnum": 84006,
          "name": "Before the Farmhouse",
          "description": "A weatherboarded farmhouse with peeling paint reeks of penury. Relentless heat buckles the wooden boards, and the front door bulges obscenely, ready to burst its frame. The front stoop, though, is graceful with a porch swing to one side and flower pots to the other -- except the peonies are desiccated.",
